            "url": "https://hongsheng-xu.github.io/2020/12/13/Hexo/0%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8HEXO%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/",
            "title": "零基础使用HEXO搭建个人博客之HEXO及其初始化",
            "date_published": "2020-12-13T04:12:45.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"hexo搭建个人博客\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#hexo搭建个人博客\">#</a> HEXO 搭建个人博客</h1>\n<h2 id=\"准备\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#准备\">#</a> 准备</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuamlhbnNodS5jb20vcC9iZWJiYTBkODAzOGU=\">安装 git</span>--<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXQtc2NtLmNvbS8=\">git 官网</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuamlhbnNodS5jb20vcC8xM2Y0NWUyNGIxZGU=\">安装 nodejs</span>--<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9ub2RlanMub3JnL2VuLw==\">nodejs 官网</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuamlhbnNodS5jb20vcC8wYzBkOGQxMGExY2I=\">注册 github</span>-- 创建一个和 Username 一样名称的仓库<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9pbWdjaHIuY29tL2kvclNOZFo4\"> &lt;img src=&quot;https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/12/08/rSNdZ8.md.png&quot; alt=&quot;创建仓库&quot;  /&gt;</span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Tips: 创建仓库名如果与 Username 不一致，请在下文初始化博客和配置博客文件时使用和仓库名一样的名字！！！<strong>访问链接 https:// 仓库名.github.io 访问</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"git\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#git\">#</a> Git</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>在任意文件里，点击鼠标右键，打开 git bash 输入配置信息</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$git</span> config --global user.name <span class=\"string\">&quot;用户名&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$git</span> config --global user.email <span class=\"string\">&quot;邮箱地址&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 例如:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$git</span> config --global user.name <span class=\"string\">&quot;hongsheng-xu&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$git</span> config --global user.email <span class=\"string\">&quot;1394948572@qq.com&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<p>在 git bash 里输入</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$ssh</span>-keygen -t rsa -C  <span class=\"string\">&quot;邮箱地址&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#例如: </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$ssh</span>-keygen -t rsa -C  <span class=\"string\">&quot;1394948572@qq.com&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>控制台输出如下:</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Enter file <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"built_in\">which</span> to save the key (/c/Users/13949/.ssh/id_rsa):</span><br><span class=\"line\">Created directory <span class=\"string\">&#x27;/c/Users/13949/.ssh&#x27;</span>.</span><br><span class=\"line\">Enter passphrase (empty <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> no passphrase):</span><br><span class=\"line\">Enter same passphrase again:</span><br><span class=\"line\">Your identification has been saved <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> /c/Users/13949/.ssh/id_rsa</span><br><span class=\"line\">Your public key has been saved <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> /c/Users/13949/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br><span class=\"line\">The key fingerprint is:</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#后文输出省略......</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># 打开目录--控制台第二行输出Created directory &#x27;/c/Users/<span class=\"number\">13949</span>/.ssh&#x27;.其中ssh的存放路径为:</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">C:\\<span class=\"title\">Users</span>\\13949\\.<span class=\"title\">ssh</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"># 打开<span class=\"title\">github</span>&gt;点击个人头像&gt;点击设置(<span class=\"title\">Settings</span>)&gt;点击<span class=\"title\">SSH</span> <span class=\"title\">and</span> <span class=\"title\">GPG</span> <span class=\"title\">keys</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">New</span> <span class=\"title\">SSH</span> <span class=\"title\">key</span>&gt;在路径:<span class=\"title\">C</span>:\\<span class=\"title\">Users</span>\\13949\\.<span class=\"title\">ssh</span>记事本打开<span class=\"title\">id_rsa.pub</span>文件,复制全部到<span class=\"title\">New</span> <span class=\"title\">SSH</span> <span class=\"title\">key</span>中<span class=\"title\">key</span>内容里</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgchr.com/i/rSdmMn\"><img data-src=\"https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/12/08/rSdmMn.md.png\" alt=\"rSdmMn.md.png\" /></a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"hexo安装\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#hexo安装\">#</a> Hexo 安装</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL3poLWNuL2RvY3Mv\">hexo 文档</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvLw==\">hexo 安装</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># 安装hexo, win+R,输入<span class=\"built_in\">cmd</span> 打开控制台输入: </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">e: </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">md</span> <span class=\"title\">blog</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">cd</span> <span class=\"title\">blog</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">npm</span> <span class=\"title\">install</span> <span class=\"title\">hexo</span>-<span class=\"title\">cli</span> -<span class=\"title\">g</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">#列如: </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">C</span>:\\<span class=\"title\">Users</span>\\13949&gt;<span class=\"title\">e</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">E</span>:\\&gt;<span class=\"title\">md</span> <span class=\"title\">blog</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">E</span>:\\&gt;<span class=\"title\">cd</span> <span class=\"title\">blog</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">E</span>:\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">npm</span> <span class=\"title\">install</span> <span class=\"title\">hexo</span>-<span class=\"title\">cli</span> -<span class=\"title\">g</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><strong>Tips: 通过上述代码在 E 盘创建了一个名为 blog 的文件夹，接下来我们需要做的就是初始化个人博客</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"hexo初始化\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#hexo初始化\">#</a> Hexo 初始化</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#在blog文件夹下初始化博客 hexo init 博客名</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo init hongsheng-xu</span><br><span class=\"line\">#进入博客所在文件夹</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> hongsheng-xu</span><br><span class=\"line\">#安装依赖</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm i</span><br><span class=\"line\">#安装插件</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm i hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class=\"line\">#运行博客</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo sever</span><br><span class=\"line\">#上一步也可以这样写--运行博客并指定端口名</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo s -p <span class=\"number\">8080</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#列如:</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">E:\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">hexo</span> <span class=\"title\">init</span> <span class=\"title\">hongsheng</span>-<span class=\"title\">xu</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">E</span>:\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">cd</span> <span class=\"title\">hongsheng</span>-<span class=\"title\">xu</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">E</span>:\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">hongsheng</span>-<span class=\"title\">xu</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">npm</span> <span class=\"title\">i</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">E</span>:\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">hongsheng</span>-<span class=\"title\">xu</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">npm</span> <span class=\"title\">i</span> <span class=\"title\">hexo</span>-<span class=\"title\">deployer</span>-<span class=\"title\">git</span> --<span class=\"title\">save</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">E</span>:\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">hongsheng</span>-<span class=\"title\">xu</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">hexo</span> <span class=\"title\">sever</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>** 输入 hexo sever 后你会看到控制台输出如下: **</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class=\"line\">#INFO  <span class=\"built_in\">Start</span> processing</span><br><span class=\"line\">#INFO  Hexo is running <span class=\"built_in\">at</span> http://localhost:<span class=\"number\">4000</span> . Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>完成这一步，nodejs 会建立一个本地服务器通常会向 Windows 请求相关权限</p>\n<p>你可以复制地址 http://localhost:4000 到浏览器的地址栏，回车就能看到个人博客啦！</p>\n<p>同时按住 ctrl+c 可以停止服务器的运行</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>搭建好的个人博客大概长这样</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgchr.com/i/rSBmMd\"><img data-src=\"https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/12/08/rSBmMd.md.png\" alt=\"个人博客\" /></a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"hexo发布至github\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#hexo发布至github\">#</a> Hexo 发布至 github</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>修改博客子目录下_config.yml</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgchr.com/i/ri3Y7T\"><img data-src=\"https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/12/10/ri3Y7T.png\" alt=\"修改_config.yml.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>修改为 https:// 仓库名.github.io    <strong>这样就可以通过仓库名.github.io 去访问个人博客</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgchr.com/i/ri3Dj1\"><img data-src=\"https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/12/10/ri3Dj1.png\" alt=\"ri3Dj1.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>找到 deploy 加入几行代码</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgchr.com/i/ri8V29\"><img data-src=\"https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/12/10/ri8V29.png\" alt=\"ri8V29.png\" /></a></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight yml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">deploy:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">type:</span> <span class=\"string\">git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">branch:</span> <span class=\"string\">master</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">repo:</span> <span class=\"string\">https://github.com/hongsheng-xu/hongsheng-xu.github.io.git</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><em>Tips:  这里 type 指定为 git,branch 指定为 master, 如果你有新建分支可以提交到其他分支上，repo 里写上自己仓库的地址 &gt; 打开 github &gt; 进入自己的博客仓库 (博客名.gthub.io 这个仓库)&gt; 点击下载 code &gt; 复制地址</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgchr.com/i/ri8XdK\"><img data-src=\"https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/12/10/ri8XdK.png\" alt=\"ri8XdK.png\" /></a></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>在博客所在的文件夹下点击右键打开 git bash 安装 hexo-deployer-git</li>\n</ol>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>编译代码 hexo g</li>\n</ol>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>上传代码 (提交到分支) hexo d</li>\n</ol>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><strong>以后就可以通过 https:// 仓库名.github.io/ 去访问个人博客了</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n",
